John Calbrese is a National Speaker and has this topic very clearly presented. I hope you can make it. He is very convincing!!

We all have the need to more about this topic!

Everyone needs money. Most people want to generate more income but struggle with the "how to" of generating enough to make ends meet. This lecture will take a closer look at what may be holding you back from acquiring the wealth you need and desire. We will discuss the blocks you may have and help to show you that YOU hold all the cards - you just need to play them correctly. With new awareness... you will find that the financial gains you seek, lay mostly in your thinking!
